Aim_usp_basement

Just a simple map of Knifes and Usp's.

You start off behind boxes, on the boxes are little forts. Just climb up the ladder. Behind you are more ladders, which lead to the 2nd floor. In the 2nd floor are boxes that you use for cover. On the 1st floor is lots of cover, includes boxes, sandbags and ammo stacks. In the middle are ramps leading to the 2nd floor and to the middle platform. On the middle platform is a grenade. (be carefull)

Have Fun!!! :)
